@startuml UC03_Sequence
title UC03: 更新个人信息 - 顺序图

actor "用户" as UserActor
boundary "个人中心界面" as ProfileForm
control "资料管理控制器" as ProfileController
entity "Student/Teacher" as UserEntity

UserActor -> ProfileForm : 更新联系信息
ProfileForm -> ProfileController : 保存请求(info)
ProfileController -> UserEntity : updateInfo(info)
UserEntity --> ProfileController : success
ProfileController --> ProfileForm : 更新成功
ProfileForm -> UserActor : 提示成功
@enduml
